cy for Health Care Policy and Research”, was executed by making the substitution for “Agency for Health Care Policy Research”, to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1998—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/362"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–362","children":[],"tail":" struck out heading and designation of subsec. (a) and heading and text of subsec. (b). Text of subsec. (b) read as follows: “Not later than "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-12-30"},"text":"December 30, 1993","children":[],"tail":", and each December 30 thereafter, the Secretary shall prepare and submit to the Committee on Energy and Commerce of the House of Representatives and the Committee on Labor and Human Resources of the Senate, a report concerning the activities carried out with the amounts referred to in subsection (a) of this section.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1995—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/66"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–66","children":[],"tail":" substituted “"},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-12-30"},"text":"December 30, 1993","children":[],"tail":", and each December 30 thereafter” for “"},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-09-30"},"text":"September 30, 1993","children":[],"tail":", and annually thereafter”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1993—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/43"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–43","children":[],"tail":" substituted “"},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-09-30"},"text":"September 30, 1993","children":[],"tail":"” for “"},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-05-03"},"text":"May 3, 1993","children":[],"tail":"”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idb58d9952-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and 